    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? I'm parting with my car, and it has been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really wonderful shape, runs smoothly, and has been super well-maintained over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this beauty won't let you down. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
