    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This unit delivers exceptional linear power through its 8,000 RPM range, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanical maintenance is up to date, with particular attention paid to the VANOS system and subframe reinforcement to ensure optimal chassis rigidity. The factory limited-slip differential provides superb corner-exit traction, while the suspension geometry remains true, offering the communicative feedback synonymous with the M-division. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains robust and the throttle response is sharp, making this an ideal candidate for the purist seeking a mechanically sound, high-performance icon.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
