    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained luxury sedan offers a perfect blend of sophisticated style and dependable performance. The exterior retains a deep, reflective shine, though minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel reflect its honest road history. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are supple and free of rips, showing only light creasing on the driver's side. All technological features\u2014including the navigation system, heated seats, and premium 12-speaker audio\u2014operate perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises, backed by a complete service log showing regular oil changes and a recent brake pad replacement. The tires have substantial tread remaining, and the car tracks straight and true. This is a solid, well-cared-for vehicle that delivers a premium driving experience without the 'new car' price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
