    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my reliable daily driver and it's looking for a great new home! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my trips around town. It drives smoothly, looks fantastic, and has clearly been well-loved. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
